                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/20/237301566/1d77b3f1972e0b02f49a1b5a27009d7c_888359372350112506.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "March 7, 2023",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Upon receiving a message from the ancient lamp out of the blue, even the Great Adventurer of the Realms, Author of the Teyvat Travel Guide, Supplier to the Renowned Lord Sangemah Bay, Elder of the Hexenzirkel, Codename \"A,\" Mother of the Most Adorable Klee — Alice was taken aback.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Fortunately, it was not a disastrous incident that had prompted the message. Instead, it served to bring back memories of companions whom she shared her youth with.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "YouTube:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    }
